## 💡 Interview Quick-Reference Table

| Tool | Scaling Dimension | Best For... | Key Constraint |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **HPA** | Horizontal (Pods) | Stateless apps, Web servers | Needs resource requests defined |
| **VPA** | Vertical (Resources) | Stateful apps (DBs) | Pod restarts required for changes |
| **KEDA** | Event-based | Jobs, Message processing | Requires a "Scaler" for the event source |
| **CA** | Nodes (Groups) | Standard cloud clusters | Limited by Node Group definitions |
| **Karpenter**| Nodes (Direct) | Diverse workloads, Cost optimization | Cloud-specific (mainly AWS) |

